"The N8N auth header is cleaned before it leaves WordPress. Characters that "
"could alter the request are stripped out."
msgstr ""
"La cabecera N8N auth se limpia antes de salir de WordPress. Se eliminan los "
"caracteres que puedan alterar la solicitud."

